default4.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultAn important part of the 
defaultcertification process is t
defaulto assess the technical competence of the contractors that are members of the competent person schemes against th
defaulte requirements set out in 
defaultDCLG’s conditions of authorisation and the 
defaultMinimum Technical Competence requirements
