defaultcompetition between the different operators of competent person schemes is a positive factor in terms of providing an element of choice for electrical contractors and keeping the cost of 
defaultcertification
default at a reasonable level. 
defaultT
defaulthe 
defaultUKAS accreditation process is aimed at ensuring the consistency of outcome
default, where there are a number of providers,
default and therefore maintaining common standards. 
