defaultWhilst DCLG maintains an overview of the competent person schemes and has ultimate responsib
defaultility for the authorisation of these schemes, the day to day assessment and supervision of the schemes is carried out by UKAS on DCLG’s behalf. The UKAS accreditation process is, of necessity, based on sample testing of the organisations concerned but is n
defaultonetheless a 
defaultrigorous
default process
default. UKAS considers that accreditation provides the necessary level of assurance of competence without being unduly intrusive or expensive. 
